First workshop using ESPD, a firmware for using PureData patches inside esp32.
The firmware is developped by Miller Pucket and the Tangible Music Lab.

This musical instrument is an experimentation using this technology, expanding my personnal research about the relation of sound and light.
There is no C# code for the ESP, only a PureDataPatch from Designing Sound, edited by Tim Taurek.

